Add a differential completeness test against a pinned CPython checkout. CI
scans the whole tree through the single shared ``ty`` session on every push and
pull request and asserts the diagnostics are a superset of a committed golden
baseline, so a regression that silently drops real, ty-resolvable violations
fails the build. Regenerate the baseline with
``scripts/regenerate-cpython-golden.sh`` (issue #192).
